      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and zero imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory, offering a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a perfect example of this model.",
